Stack OVERFLOW
Stack Overflow
in Stack:-
Stack Overflow occurs when 
we try to insert (PUSH) an 
element into a stack that is 
already full.
A stack has a fixed 
maximum size. When the 
value of top = max − 1, the 
stack is full. If we try to 
PUSH another element, 
there is no space available, 
so STACK OVERFLOW
happens.
