Application of stack
3. Memory Management
Stack is used to store temporary data and local variables of functions. When the 
function ends, the memory is automatically removed from the stack.
4. Function Calls (Call Stack)
Stack is used to manage function calls. When a function is called, its data is pushed    
into the   stack. When the function finishes, it is popped from the stack. This follows 
LIFO principle.
2. Expression Evaluation and Conversion
Stack is used to convert and evaluate expressions like infix, postfix, and prefix. 
It helps in solving expressions correctly using operator precedence.
1.Recursion
Stack is used in recursion to store function calls and their data. This is called 
the call stack.
When a recursive function is called, its information is pushed into the stack. 
When the function finishes, it is popped from the stack.
