In postfix expression, operator 
comes after operands. It is 
evaluated using a stack. We scan 
the expression from left to right. 
When an operand is found, it is 
pushed into the stack. When an 
operator is found, two operands 
are popped from the stack, the 
operation is performed, and the 
result is pushed back into the 
stack. The final answer will be on 
the top of the stack.
Evaluation of Postfix Expression 
