1.Simple and easy to use
Stack operations like push and pop are simple to implement.
2. Fast operations
Insertion and deletion take O(1) time (constant time).
3. Useful in recursion
Stack manages function calls using the call stack.
4. Helps in expression evaluation
Used for infix, postfix, and prefix conversion and evaluation
.
5. Used in undo/redo operations
Applications like MS Word and browsers use stack.
Advantages of Stack
